                        <interp inst="t18670128-name-32" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE FARRANCE</persName>
                  </hi> (762 A). I was present in December, 1865, when the prisoner was convicted in the name of <persName id="t18670128-name-33">
                     <interp inst="t18670128-name-33" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
                     <rs id="t18670128-alias-1" type="alias">
