                  </persName>—I produce a certificate. (<hi rend="italic">Read:—Central Criminal Court. James Hayes, convicted of un<lb></lb>lawfully uttering counterfeit coin.—Confined Nine Months.</hi>) I am sure the prisoner is the man.</p>
